      <title>巴菲特斥资 5.9 亿美元购买西方石油公司股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/buffett-backs-occidental-deal-with-590-million-stock-purchase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西方石油公司 (Occidental Petroleum Corp.) 同意收购私人二叠纪生产商 CrownRock LP，这是今年最大的能源交易之一，伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 本周购买了价值近 5.9 亿美元的西方石油公司 (Occidental Petroleum Corp.) 股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/buffett-backs-occidental-deal-with-590-million-stock-purchase</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 02:18:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注美联储转向，美元跌至八月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周四跌至四个月低点，因为交易员消化了迄今为止最明确的信号，即美联储激进的加息行动已经结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/dollar-drops-to-weakest-since-august-as-fed-weighs-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 01:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街交易员全力以赴迎接 2024 年的重大货币转向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/wall-street-traders-go-all-in-on-great-monetary-pivot-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过近年来的冲突后，华尔街交易员和美联储有史以来第一次大体同步：伟大的货币转向即将到来，央行官员们正在为世界最大经济体实现曾经不可想象的软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/wall-street-traders-go-all-in-on-great-monetary-pivot-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 00:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储后全球股市和国债延续涨势：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储明年降息后，亚洲股市和债券也跟随全球股市上涨，随着通胀缓解，重新点燃了整个市场的看涨脉搏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
