    <item>
      <title>美联储降息导致 10 年期国债收益率跌破 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/traders-add-to-bet-on-interest-rate-cuts-in-2024-on-fed-forecast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[10 年期美国国债收益率自 8 月以来首次跌破 4%，交易员注意到美联储已结束加息的信号，加大了 2024 年更大幅度降息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/traders-add-to-bet-on-interest-rate-cuts-in-2024-on-fed-forecast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 19:14:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国米其林星级餐厅名单新增四家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/thailand-s-roster-of-michelin-star-rated-restaurants-grows-with-four-additions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[又有四家泰国餐厅获得米其林星级评级，成为越来越多的餐厅名单中的一员，新一代年轻而充满激情的厨师帮助提升了这个东南亚国家的美食吸引力，获得了令人垂涎的认可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/thailand-s-roster-of-michelin-star-rated-restaurants-grows-with-four-additions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 10:48:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元违约几周后碧桂园支付人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/country-garden-said-to-remit-funds-to-fully-repay-yuan-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十月份发生美元债券违约的中国开发商碧桂园控股有限公司周三全额偿还了人民币票据，同一天，一位住房高级官员表示，国家将避免房地产公司出现一系列拖欠债务的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-13/country-garden-said-to-remit-funds-to-fully-repay-yuan-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 09:42:42 GMT</pubDate>
